column5: Got somebody's outdoors card in the mail today....looks like you used to live here, but they don't have or didn't process your change of address. So if your name is Brian and you used to live in the J section of Brampton and haven't received your card, I have it.  I'll hang on to it for a couple days just in case you see this, then throw it in the mail and send it back to Peterborough. Just drop me a line on the board....PM's go right to my phone.
My name is Brian,and I did live in Brampton in the early 80,s,but that was when Brampton was Brampton,and Bramalea had sections with the Alphabet. LOL  So is that whole area now Brampton?
Soon as the b'y left, they fixed it up?
Yes, I guess it's technically Bramalea....or Bramaladesh....or something like that
